            <div>
              <CheckIcon />
            </div>
            <span>Entrega en <span class="text-green-500">5 días</span></span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-5 flex justify-center">
          <Boton> Solicitar servicio </Boton>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-lg p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-white/20 flex flex-col justify-between h-full
  transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-white/40"
      >
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">Plan Avanzado</h3>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold top-0">
          <span class="text-4xl"> S/ 1,500.00</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2 text-[20px]">
          Perfecto para negocios que buscan destacar y generar clientes
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 text-gray-300">
          <li
            class="flex items-start text-left text-[18px] gap-2 py-4 border-t-2 border-gray-500 first:border-t-0"
